-- Errani Beats Former Champion Ivanovic in French Open Third Round
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-06-01T11:11:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-01/errani-beats-former-champion-ivanovic-in-french-open-third-round.html
Italy’s Sara Errani defeated former
champion Ana Ivanovic in three sets in the third round of
tennis’s French Open.  Errani, the 21st seed, won 1-6, 7-5, 6-3 at  Roland Garros 
in Paris. Ivanovic, the No. 13 seed from Serbia, won the French
Open in 2008.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  